HEADWORD: Iodoformogen
<hw>I`o*do*for"mo*gen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Iodoform</ets> + <ets>-gen</ets> root of
<grk>gi`gnesqai</grk> to be born.]</ety> <fld>(Pharm.)</fld> <def>A
